01:55:59,007 --> 01:56:01,008
Hmm.

1045
01:56:22,280 --> 01:56:23,614
Hey, pretty girl.

1046
01:56:25,200 --> 01:56:27,201
Time to wake up.

1047
01:58:04,132 --> 01:58:07,718
- Where have you been?
- What do you want?

1048
01:58:07,802 --> 01:58:11,054
My lamp and dishes.

1049
01:58:12,515 --> 01:58:15,350
Come on, Diane. It's been three weeks.

1050
01:58:17,145 --> 01:58:20,606
I put your dishes in that box.

1051
01:58:40,919 --> 01:58:44,212
- That's my ashtray.
- Take it.

1052
01:58:55,183 --> 01:58:57,559
Anytime.

1053
01:58:57,644 --> 01:59:00,270
I'm just making sure, Diane.

1054
01:59:09,989 --> 01:59:11,531
This is it?

1055
01:59:11,616 --> 01:59:13,200
Yeah.

1056
01:59:17,664 --> 01:59:21,208
Oh, by the way, those two detectives
came by again looking for you.

1057
02:00:15,096 --> 02:00:17,222
Camilla.

1058
02:00:19,142 --> 02:00:21,601
You've come back.

1059
02:02:03,162 --> 02:02:06,289
What was that you were saying, beautiful?

1060
02:02:07,375 --> 02:02:09,668
I said...

1061
02:02:09,752 --> 02:02:11,753
"You drive me wild."

1062
02:02:24,934 --> 02:02:26,893
We shouldn't do this anymore.

1063
02:02:33,776 --> 02:02:35,735
Don't say that.

1064
02:02:40,908 --> 02:02:43,577
Don't ever say that.

1065
02:02:43,661 --> 02:02:45,996
Don't, Diane.

1066
02:02:46,080 --> 02:02:48,957
Stop it! Diane, stop!

1067
02:02:50,209 --> 02:02:52,586
I've tried to tell you this before.

1068
02:03:01,762 --> 02:03:04,055
It's him, isn't it?

1069
02:03:14,775 --> 02:03:17,819
Now, I'm not trying
to show you how to do the scene.

1070
02:03:17,904 --> 02:03:20,488
But just... watch me...

1071
02:03:20,573 --> 02:03:22,699
and I think you'll understand
what I'm getting at.

1072
02:03:22,783 --> 02:03:24,701
Hank.

1073
02:03:27,580 --> 02:03:29,915
Don't sit so... rigid.

1074
02:03:29,999 --> 02:03:32,709
Just – Just relax.

1075
02:03:32,793 --> 02:03:35,545
Now, the two of you are alone...

1076
02:03:35,630 --> 02:03:37,756
and it's real comfortable...

1077
02:03:39,300 --> 02:03:42,052
like you've known each other forever.

1078
02:03:42,136 --> 02:03:45,138
Even if you don't say anything,
it's-it's real comfortable.

1079
02:03:47,266 --> 02:03:49,184
Hank, can you just clear the set?

1080
02:03:49,268 --> 02:03:51,937
There's too many people around here.
Let us get this worked out.

1081
02:03:52,021 --> 02:03:54,522
Clear the set!
Clear the set, please!

1082
02:03:54,607 --> 02:03:56,650
Everyone have a cup of coffee.

1083
02:03:56,734 --> 02:04:00,153
- Everyone, please!
- Can Diane stay?

1084
02:04:00,238 --> 02:04:02,447
Yeah, sure. Diane can stay.

1085
02:04:02,531 --> 02:04:05,575
- Um, Hank, let Diane stay.
- Diane?

1086
02:04:11,874 --> 02:04:13,792
Now, when she starts to cry...

1087
02:04:13,876 --> 02:04:15,835
don't pull her towards you.

1088
02:04:17,505 --> 02:04:19,756
Let her fall into you.

1089
02:04:20,800 --> 02:04:22,759
Just let her fall.

1090
02:04:26,264 --> 02:04:28,223
Now, when you kiss her...

1091
02:04:29,684 --> 02:04:32,727
it's just a continuation of that move.

1092
02:04:34,563 --> 02:04:36,523
There's no break.

1093
02:05:02,550 --> 02:05:04,092
Kill the lights!

1094
02:05:13,894 --> 02:05:15,854
Don't be mad.

1095
02:05:15,938 --> 02:05:19,274
- Don't make it be like this.
- Oh, sure.

1096
02:05:19,358 --> 02:05:22,068
You want me to make this
easy for you? No.

1097
02:05:22,153 --> 02:05:25,238
No fucking way! It's not gonna be!

1098
02:05:25,323 --> 02:05:27,991
- It's not easy for me!
- Diane!

1099
02:06:52,201 --> 02:06:54,119
Hello, it's me.

1100
02:06:54,203 --> 02:06:56,329
Leave a message.

1101
02:06:58,374 --> 02:07:00,333
Diane?

1102
02:07:04,672 --> 02:07:07,549
- Hello?
- Diane?

1103
02:07:09,301 --> 02:07:13,430
- Camilla.
- Diane, the car's waiting.

1104
02:07:13,514 --> 02:07:15,473
Are you okay?

1105
02:07:15,558 --> 02:07:17,517
You coming?

1106
02:07:21,730 --> 02:07:25,108
- Uh-huh.
- Good.

1107
02:07:25,192 --> 02:07:27,110
It means so much to me.

1108
02:07:28,362 --> 02:07:30,989
Go on. The car's
right outside your house.

1109
02:07:32,199 --> 02:07:34,117
It's been waiting, okay?

1110
02:07:39,248 --> 02:07:41,124
Okay.

1111
02:07:41,208 --> 02:07:44,752
It's 6980 Mulholland Drive.

1112
02:07:46,213 --> 02:07:48,131
Mulholland Drive.

1113
02:08:57,826 --> 02:09:01,120
What are you doing?
We don't stop here.

1114
02:09:05,834 --> 02:09:08,253
A surprise.

1115
02:09:30,985 --> 02:09:32,944
Shortcut.

1116
02:09:35,281 --> 02:09:36,614
Come on, sweetheart.

1117
02:09:43,038 --> 02:09:45,248
It's beautiful.

1118
02:09:45,332 --> 02:09:47,208
A secret path.

1119
02:10:54,401 --> 02:10:56,402
Ah. Perfect timing.

1120
02:10:58,072 --> 02:11:00,031
Welcome, Diane.

1121
02:11:06,038 --> 02:11:07,538
Well...

1122
02:11:08,540 --> 02:11:10,583
here's to love.

1123
02:11:20,010 --> 02:11:21,511
Here's to love.

1124
02:11:26,934 --> 02:11:28,768
Ah, here she is.

1125
02:11:30,604 --> 02:11:32,522
Oh.

1126
02:11:38,320 --> 02:11:40,405
I don't believe you met my mother.

1127
02:11:41,949 --> 02:11:44,450
Hi. I'm Diane Selwyn.

1128
02:11:44,535 --> 02:11:47,203
Well, just call me Coco.
Everybody does.

1129
02:11:47,287 --> 02:11:49,706
Pleased to meet you.
Well, let's eat.

1130
02:11:49,790 --> 02:11:51,791
I'm starving.

1131
02:11:57,840 --> 02:12:00,133
I'm sorry I was late.

1132
02:12:19,820 --> 02:12:22,655
I'm from Deep River, Ontario.

1133
02:12:23,574 --> 02:12:25,450
A small town.

1134
02:12:25,534 --> 02:12:29,120
So you rolled in here from Canada.

1135
02:12:30,330 --> 02:12:32,665
I always wanted to come here.

1136
02:12:33,876 --> 02:12:36,586
I won this jitterbug contest.

1137
02:12:37,755 --> 02:12:39,672
That sort of led to acting.

1138
02:12:41,467 --> 02:12:44,010
You know, wanting to act.

1139
02:12:45,512 --> 02:12:47,513
When my aunt died –

1140
02:12:49,349 --> 02:12:52,935
Anyway, she – she left me some money.

1141
02:12:53,020 --> 02:12:55,688
- She worked here.
- In the movies?

1142
02:12:56,857 --> 02:12:58,524
Yes.

1143
02:12:59,526 --> 02:13:02,028
Well, how did you meet Camilla?

1144
02:13:03,697 --> 02:13:05,948
On The Sylvia North Story.

1145
02:13:06,033 --> 02:13:07,950
Oh, Camilla was great in that.

1146
02:13:19,922 --> 02:13:21,506
Yeah.

1147
02:13:23,217 --> 02:13:26,219
I wanted the lead so bad.

1148
02:13:27,471 --> 02:13:30,139
Anyway, Camilla got the part.

1149
02:13:33,560 --> 02:13:36,062
The director –

1150
02:13:36,146 --> 02:13:38,397
Bob Brooker?

1151
02:13:38,482 --> 02:13:40,066
Yes.

1152
02:13:42,653 --> 02:13:44,612
He didn't think so much of me.

1153
02:13:49,618 --> 02:13:52,703
Anyway, that's when we became friends.

1154
02:13:53,914 --> 02:13:55,832
She helped me...

1155
02:13:55,916 --> 02:13:59,418
getting some parts in some of her films.

1156
02:14:01,380 --> 02:14:02,922
I see.

1157
02:14:18,021 --> 02:14:20,731
So I got the pool...

1158
02:14:20,816 --> 02:14:22,859
and she got the pool man.

1159
02:14:22,943 --> 02:14:26,028
I couldn't believe it.

1160
02:14:26,113 --> 02:14:29,115
I wanted to buy that judge a Rolls-Royce.

1161
02:14:36,039 --> 02:14:37,957
Sometimes good things happen.

1162
02:15:32,054 --> 02:15:34,347
So I guess we've saved the best for last.

1163
02:15:37,351 --> 02:15:39,268
Do you wanna tell them?

1164
02:15:39,353 --> 02:15:41,270
No, y-you tell them.

1165
02:15:45,525 --> 02:15:47,443
Camilla and I ...

1166
02:16:00,040 --> 02:16:02,041
are going to be –

1167
02:16:13,929 --> 02:16:16,889
Sorry about that.

1168
02:16:23,271 --> 02:16:25,231
No, I'm fine.

1169
02:16:31,822 --> 02:16:33,656
This is the girl.

1170
02:16:35,409 --> 02:16:38,494
Don't show me this fuckin' thing here.

1171
02:16:38,578 --> 02:16:42,498
It's just an actress' photo resume.
Everybody's got one.

1172
02:16:43,917 --> 02:16:46,377
You got the money?

1173
02:16:46,461 --> 02:16:48,045
I sure do.

1174
02:16:59,599 --> 02:17:03,894
Okay, now, once you hand that over to me,
it's a done deal.

1175
02:17:06,815 --> 02:17:08,691
You sure you want this?

1176
02:17:14,448 --> 02:17:16,866
More than anything in this world.

1177
02:17:27,836 --> 02:17:31,130
When it's finished,
you'll find this where I told you.

1178
02:17:44,603 --> 02:17:46,520
What's it open?

1179
02:22:12,912 --> 02:22:15,289
Silencio.

